{"tid":509189,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解個個都要講 Merry Christmas?","createTime":"2017-12-25T04:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T08:34:02.000Z","uid":27410,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88e265370c3d5b444cde71503a993ddc12a7d6cf","tid":509189,"uid":27410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"又唔係個個都信耶教<br />\n唔明點解一到聖誕 個個都講 Merry Christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聖誕係班教徒慶祝佢地 教主 生日啊<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係耶教 有人同你講 Merry Christmas<br />\n你可以就咁回佢 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Thank You </span></span><br />\n又或者 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Happy Holidays / Happy Red Day</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Say &ldquo;Thank You&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\nJust because <span style=\"color: red;\">someone wishes you a Merry Christmas doesn&rsquo;t mean you have to say it back</span>. It would probably feel quite unnatural for you to say it back, so that probably isn&rsquo;t the right move. <span style=\"color: red;\">A simple &ldquo;thank you&rdquo; will certainly suffice</span>. It acknowledges the gesture while offering a friendly response. In helps prevent the situation from becoming awkward.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Say &ldquo;Happy Holidays&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\nAnother simple way to prevent this from becoming an issue is by saying &ldquo;Happy Holidays&rdquo; in return. This is a very general term, which means that almost anyone can relate to it. People will likely appreciate the gesture, and you can both go along on your way.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.themonastery.org/blog/2016/01/how-should-you-respond-to-merry-christmas-if-you-dont-celebrate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themonastery.org%2Fblog%2F2016%2F01%2Fhow-should-you-respond-to-merry-christmas-if-you-dont-celebrate%2F&d=G1UKlA4RetlnJaYBf7VjbO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=2c8a34be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.themonastery.org/blog/2016/01/how-should-you-respond-to-merry-christmas-if-you-dont-celebrate/</a>"},{"pid":"21d8ec0feb6a1b11635fd52259de8c5d664d30cb","tid":509189,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"個個都merry christmas唔通個個都merry咩"},{"pid":"d6075f58c27abc46344a0c68d9e12a0e90ee28b3","tid":509189,"uid":27410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"我諗香港人應該係慶祝紅日 有假放 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHappy Red Day!"},{"pid":"289bcfaae5cf8104a594bb78effc21b6e13427bc","tid":509189,"uid":27410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"有耶撚偷偷留下負評"},{"pid":"f60b90ba026de2b47e87265ca407fc592038e66f","tid":509189,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"同大陸一樣反聖誕呀？"},{"pid":"a02ec9e2d5ee23380c767b996362596646782005","tid":509189,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"同啲左膠話講merry christmas冒犯回撚有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6791fdd4a68524c46531d07f927fdc56f726f38f","tid":509189,"uid":7071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:07:33.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"41d6094d4d4afa3ff467a5662e98427f2976abe9","tid":509189,"uid":2156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f60b90ba026de2b47e87265ca407fc592038e66f","tid":509189,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"同大陸一樣反聖誕呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"耶呢就反開嘅，唔洗話跟大陸乜柒<br />\n<br />\n不過港豬有假放話之佢慶祝啲咩<br />\n端午節快樂都得啦，差在未講清明節快樂架啫"},{"p